libosdp provides CMake targets:

  find_package(LibOSDP CONFIG REQUIRED)

  # to link to shared library
  target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE libosdp::osdp)

  # or, to link to static library
  target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE libosdp::osdpstatic)

libosdp provides pkg-config modules:

    # Open Supervised Device Protocol (OSDP) Library
    libosdp
